{"tid":838001,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半對你愈好 你愈大壓力","createTime":"2018-09-26T19:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T02:20:50.000Z","uid":139763,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a72911cf6eb6c334a39b01075df27e2c0331a7a0","tid":838001,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T19:56:39.000Z","msg":"正常人會想有一個對自己好嘅另一半<br />\n但當佢真係對你太好<br />\n例如次次食飯睇戲對方出錢<br />\n會買好貴嘅禮物畀你<br />\n你唔夠錢洗仲畀錢你<br />\n呢啲好到好似父母先做嘅行為<br />\n其實會造成好大壓力<br />\n又唔知自己遲啲有冇能力還畀佢<br />\n又或者根本未認定對方係終生伴侶<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬 你咁搞法如果第時分手我會好內疚<br />\n好似欠咗你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb163084435e9bc4ed02307e57bbe3f054d1975","tid":838001,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T19:58:00.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4609badda5f0ab507217e7087c411fa32539eca9","tid":838001,"uid":208364,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T19:58:07.000Z","msg":"你未認定佢？"},{"pid":"9b5995b3b0001972ebb0d1087ed28f927c583b21","tid":838001,"uid":170867,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T19:59:53.000Z","msg":"你唔夠愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab9753124d58096aef5995a076f3cd67e6457fa","tid":838001,"uid":209301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"結婚啦"},{"pid":"cf1f566d8c5161a08fabf029b5900462fa484e32","tid":838001,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"唔夠愛囉"},{"pid":"6060c98d1b7c15bd51df63ef7bbc6d1f57ad9f88","tid":838001,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:54:50.000Z","msg":"未認定佢又同人一齊？"},{"pid":"53d522c71dadbb2d546595b8d6e44f720ab585c6","tid":838001,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"心虛？"},{"pid":"35af0fa1